name beamertheme-gotham
category Package
revision 78692
shortdesc A modern, minimal-ish, versatile and extendable yet robust theme for Beamer
longdesc This package provides a modern, minimal-ish, versatile, LaTeX3
longdesc and extendable yet robust Beamer theme with some lines of code
longdesc gathered or borrowed from other themes. It uses the l3build
longdesc system to both build and verify (Test-Driven Development) the
longdesc delivered code. "Gotham" tries to bring higher flexibility
longdesc thanks to LaTeX3 implementation on top of the good-looking
longdesc Metropolis theme.
